<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Purpose and Impact GmbH</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #2c5f2d;
            --primary-light: #4a7c4e;
            --secondary: #97bc62;
            --accent: #1e3d19;
            --light: #f4f7f0;
            --dark: #141a12;
            --gray: #6b7280;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --card-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(20,40,18,0.06), 0 16px 40px rgba(20,40,18,0.08);
            --card-shadow-hover: 0 4px 16px rgba(20,40,18,0.1), 0 32px 64px rgba(20,40,18,0.14);
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.65;
            color: var(--dark);
            background: var(--light);
            font-size: 16px;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* ── Custom cursor ── */
        .cursor-dot {
            width: 8px; height: 8px;
            background: var(--primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: fixed;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 9999;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transition: transform 0.1s, opacity 0.3s;
        }
        .cursor-ring {
            width: 32px; height: 32px;
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(44,95,45,0.45);
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: fixed;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 9998;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transition: width 0.3s, height 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
        }
        body:hover .cursor-dot { opacity: 1; }

        /* ── Scroll reveal ── */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(36px);
            transition: opacity 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1), transform 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1);
        }
        .reveal.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        .reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
        .reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
        .reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
        .reveal-delay-4 { transition-delay: 0.4s; }

        /* ── Header ── */
        header {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
            padding: 1.1rem 2.5rem;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }
        header.scrolled {
            border-color: rgba(44,95,45,0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(20,40,18,0.07);
        }

        .header-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 46px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        .logo:hover { opacity: 0.82; }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.25rem;
        }

        nav a {
            color: var(--gray);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            padding: 0.45rem 0.95rem;
            border-radius: 100px;
            transition: color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
            background: rgba(44,95,45,0.07);
        }

        /* ── Hero ── */
        .hero {
            padding: 172px 2rem 120px;
            background:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 70% 30%, rgba(151,188,98,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%),
                linear-gradient(150deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--primary) 55%, #3a7a3b 100%);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Animated organic blobs */
        .hero-blob {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.07;
            animation: blob-drift 14s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .hero-blob:nth-child(1) {
            width: 680px; height: 680px;
            top: -200px; right: -180px;
            background: var(--secondary);
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }
        .hero-blob:nth-child(2) {
            width: 420px; height: 420px;
            bottom: -160px; left: -100px;
            background: #fff;
            animation-delay: -5s;
        }
        .hero-blob:nth-child(3) {
            width: 280px; height: 280px;
            top: 30%; left: 20%;
            background: var(--secondary);
            animation-delay: -9s;
        }

        @keyframes blob-drift {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
            33% { transform: translate(24px, -20px) scale(1.04); }
            66% { transform: translate(-18px, 14px) scale(0.97); }
        }

        /* Leaf particle canvas */
        #leaf-canvas {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 780px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero-eyebrow {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fade-up 0.9s 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) forwards;
        }
        .hero-eyebrow::before {
            content: '';
            width: 6px; height: 6px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--secondary);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.08;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fade-up 0.9s 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) forwards;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.1875rem;
            opacity: 0;
            max-width: 580px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.84);
            animation: fade-up 0.9s 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) forwards;
        }

        .hero-scroll-hint {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 2rem;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fade-up 1s 1.1s ease forwards;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .scroll-line {
            width: 1px;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.5), transparent);
            animation: scroll-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes scroll-pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scaleY(1); opacity: 0.5; }
            50% { transform: scaleY(0.6); opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes fade-up {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* ── Section divider ── */
        .section-divider {
            width: 100%;
            height: 80px;
            background: var(--light);
            position: relative;
        }
        .section-divider svg {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
        }

        /* ── Sections ── */
        section {
            padding: 110px 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-label {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            background: rgba(44, 95, 45, 0.1);
            color: var(--primary);
            padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.07em;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }
        .section-label::before {
            content: '';
            width: 5px; height: 5px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--primary);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
            font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            line-height: 1.15;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 1.0625rem;
            margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
            max-width: 560px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        /* ── Cards ── */
        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.75rem;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1), box-shadow 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(44,95,45,0.06);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(44,95,45,0.03) 0%, transparent 60%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow-hover);
        }
        .card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .card-icon {
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-light) 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(44,95,45,0.25);
            transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1), box-shadow 0.3s;
        }
        .card:hover .card-icon {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-4deg);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(44,95,45,0.35);
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.3125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        .card p {
            color: var(--gray);
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
            line-height: 1.75;
            font-size: 0.9875rem;
        }

        .card .cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            transition: gap 0.25s;
        }
        .card .cta:hover { gap: 0.7rem; }

        /* ── Testimonials ── */
        .testimonials-section {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 80px 2rem;
            border-radius: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(20,40,18,0.04), 0 12px 40px rgba(20,40,18,0.06);
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .testimonials-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .testimonials-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .testimonial {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 2rem 2rem 1.75rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            position: relative;
            border: 1px solid rgba(44,95,45,0.06);
            transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1), box-shadow 0.35s;
        }
        .testimonial:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(20,40,18,0.09);
        }

        .testimonial::before {
            content: '\201C';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0.75rem;
            right: 1.25rem;
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
            color: var(--secondary);
            opacity: 0.35;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .stars {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
        }
        .stars span {
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        .testimonial-text {
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            font-size: 0.9875rem;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        .testimonial-author {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
        }

        .testimonial-role {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .testimonial-author-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        }

        .linkedin-icon {
            width: 17px; height: 17px;
            opacity: 0.55;
            transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
        }
        .linkedin-icon:hover {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1.15);
        }

        .testimonials-label {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2.75rem;
        }
        .testimonials-label h3 {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.01em;
        }

        /* ── Contact ── */
        .contact-section {
            background:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 80% 20%, rgba(151,188,98,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
                var(--dark);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 110px 2rem;
        }

        .contact-inner {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-section .section-label {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: var(--secondary);
        }
        .contact-section .section-label::before {
            background: var(--secondary);
        }

        .contact-section .section-title {
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .contact-section .section-subtitle {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.58);
        }

        .contact-form {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 24px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-form p:first-child {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
        }

        .contact-form a {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--secondary) !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(151,188,98,0.35);
            border-radius: 14px;
            transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }
        .contact-form a:hover {
            background: rgba(151,188,98,0.12);
            border-color: rgba(151,188,98,0.6);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* ── Footer ── */
        footer {
            background: #0d1209;
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 4.5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.25rem;
        }

        .profile-photo {
            width: 96px; height: 96px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 3px solid var(--secondary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(151,188,98,0.15), 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s;
        }
        .profile-photo:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(151,188,98,0.22), 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        .footer-name {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }

        .footer-company {
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .imprint {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38);
            line-height: 1.9;
        }

        /* ── Progress bar ── */
        #progress-bar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            height: 2.5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary), var(--primary));
            z-index: 2000;
            width: 0%;
            transition: width 0.1s linear;
        }

        /* ── Responsive ── */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.25rem; }
            .hero p { font-size: 1rem; }
            .hero { padding: 150px 1.5rem 90px; }
            nav { display: none; }
            section { padding: 70px 1.5rem; }
            .section-title { font-size: 1.85rem; }
            .testimonials-section,
            .contact-section { padding: 70px 1.5rem; }
            .card { padding: 2rem; }
            .cursor-dot, .cursor-ring { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Cursor -->
    <div class="cursor-dot" id="cursorDot"></div>
    <div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

    <!-- Reading progress -->
    <div id="progress-bar"></div>

    <header id="site-header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <img src="Purpose and Impact GmbH - logo.png" alt="Purpose and Impact GmbH" class="logo">
            <nav>
                <a href="#housing">Housing</a>
                <a href="#research">Research</a>
                <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <canvas id="leaf-canvas"></canvas>
        <div class="hero-blob"></div>
        <div class="hero-blob"></div>
        <div class="hero-blob"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-eyebrow">Graz, Austria</div>
            <h1>Purpose and Impact GmbH</h1>
            <p>We support researchers on their journey, whether finding the perfect home or validating their innovations for the market.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-scroll-hint">
            <div class="scroll-line"></div>
            Scroll
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Housing Section -->
    <section id="housing">
        <span class="section-label reveal">Housing</span>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">Furnished Housing for Researchers</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2">Fully furnished apartments in Graz, designed specifically for PhD students and researchers.</p>

        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
                <div class="card-icon">🏠</div>
                <h3>Furnished Apartments</h3>
                <p>We offer fully equipped apartments in Graz, ready to move in, comfortable, and conveniently located near universities.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="cta">Request apartment →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
                <div class="card-icon">✨</div>
                <h3>Full Service Support</h3>
                <p>From viewing to move in, we guide you through the entire process so you can focus on what matters most: your research.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="cta">Book consultation →</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonials-section reveal">
            <div class="testimonials-inner">
                <div class="testimonials-label">
                    <h3>What Our Tenants Say</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonials-grid">
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="stars"><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span></div>
                        <p class="testimonial-text">Thanks to Purpose and Impact, I found a beautiful furnished apartment within just a few days. The service was incredibly fast and helpful!</p>
                        <div class="testimonial-author-row">
                            <p class="testimonial-author">Leonardo Dipilato</p>
                            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/leonardo-dipilato-512a42167/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                                <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/174/174857.png" alt="LinkedIn" class="linkedin-icon">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <p class="testimonial-role">PhD student from Italy, TU Graz</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="stars"><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span></div>
                        <p class="testimonial-text">As an international PhD student, apartment hunting was overwhelming at first. The team provided wonderful support and now I feel right at home.</p>
                        <div class="testimonial-author-row">
                            <p class="testimonial-author">Simone Giansanti</p>
                            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/simone-giansanti-6839b2329/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                                <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/174/174857.png" alt="LinkedIn" class="linkedin-icon">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <p class="testimonial-role">PhD student, Uni Graz</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Research to Market Section -->
    <section id="research">
        <span class="section-label reveal">Research to Market</span>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">From Research to Market</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2">Validation and support for researchers who want to bring their ideas to market.</p>

        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
                <div class="card-icon">📊</div>
                <h3>Market Validation</h3>
                <p>We help you understand if your research or inventions are commercially viable through thorough analysis and honest feedback.</p>
                <a href="#contact" class="cta">Start consultation →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
                <div class="card-icon">🚀</div>
